            <span class="utterance" who="#schlaefrigF" start="889.069" end="x">That happened in my house, to other parties [tenants?], while with me personally they contented themselves to take with them whatever they found in the strong-box, and some other valuables.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="900.435" end="x">Yes . . .</span>
