                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Friedrich Schlaefrig</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#schlaefrigF" start="4426.190" end="x">And so, in order to present this [one word not clear] village with complete reality, stores were opened, and the inmates of the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ghetto">ghetto</a> were able to but all kinds of things that were allotted to these stores.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
