            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Friedrich Schlaefrig</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#schlaefrigF" start="4846.992" end="x">Every week transports were sent away, with the exception of a short spell during Christmas time and Easter time. With the exception of these two periods, there were always transports sent to Poland; from the various regions of Germany and Czechoslovakia [Spool ends in middle of the sentence. Continuation on Spool 69 which had to be reproduced anew from the 'carbon wire' original. —D.P.B.]</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
