                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Friedrich Schlaefrig</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#schlaefrigF" start="x" end="x">These deportations were unpredictable. Nobody knew whether he would be put in one of the near transports. One could only surmise from a certain . . . from a certain activity in the offices of the management that transports were in the offing, and then 'one nice evening' this business . . . this was set in action.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
