                <span class="">Friedrich Schlaefrig</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#schlaefrigF" start="x" end="x">It was not known that the people were going to their death. That was not known in <a class="placename" href="#vothC110" type="camp">Theresienstadt</a>.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
