            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="x" end="x">Mrs. Schlaefrig, now you say a few words, Do you want me to see your daughter in Windsor?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class=""></span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who=" #schlaefrigFa" start="x" end="x">I ask you very kindly if you could talk to my daughter . . . [she apparently weeps] My daughter . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="x" end="x">Say something to you daughter.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class=""></span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who=" #schlaefrigFa" start="x" end="x">Dear Mieze. We are now [??] in <a class="placename" href="#vothL13">Paris</a>, and are expecting to get the visa to South Africa, and we hope that we shall see each other there real soon . . . , since you, too, are coming over . . . [pause] I send you these greetings through Dr. Boder from <a class="placename" href="#vothL256">Chicago</a>.</span>
        </li>
            </ul>
    <ol class="notes">
                
